{"title":"贝贝的加密工作","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1551","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>    贝贝找了一份为一些文件的某些部分加密的工作，加密的部分是一串小写英文字母，加密的规则是这样的：要是连续出现相同的字母，则把他们替换成这个字母的大写形式，后面紧跟相同字母的个数，并把它之前跟之后的两段字串调换，例如出现bcaaaaaaef，则新字符串变成：efA6bc，然后重新扫描字串，直到没有出现相同小写字母为止。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>    原始字符串（长度不大于250）。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 新字符串。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入1：bcaaaaaaef</p>\n<p>输入2：cmmmcefffg</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>    输出1：efA6bc</p>\n<p>    输出2：gM3cF3ce</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>数据无问题，别反馈</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}